Early Symptoms of Oral Cancer 
Early detection and timely treatment can significantly improve the chances of successful outcomes in managing oral cancer.The “3-week rule” in cancer is a guideline used by healthcare professionals to indicate the urgency of investigating and diagnosing potential cancer in patients presenting with certain symptoms. It suggests that if a patient has specific symptoms that could be indicative of cancer, and these symptoms persist or worsen for three weeks or longer, they should be promptly evaluated for possible malignancy

Inflammation is how the body responds to an injury, allergen, or an infection. It’s why a sprained ankle doubles in size and why you run a fever when your body is fighting a virus. But sometimes the body sees certain foods  as an irritant. 
When the body identifies a food as an irritant, it can cause the immune system to go on the attack and, in turn, lead to inflammation. And regularly eating inflammatory foods can damage tissue and raise your risk for various health conditions.

Let your immune system treat your cancer 

In cancer, the immune system fails, cells of the immune system fail to recognize the cancer cells. The immune system doesn’t see tumors as dangerous or foreign and doesn’t mount a strong attack against them. Another reason tumors may not stimulate an immune response is that cancer cells develop ways to escape the immune system.

A dendritic cell is a special type of immune cell that boosts immune responses in our body, by showing antigens on its surface to other cells of the immune system. 

Dendritic cells identify cancer cells, process them into bits, and jumpstart the immune response by bringing the cancer cells to the attention of the rest of the immune system.  

Dendritic cells are Immune cells that help in the Immune-recognition process, absent in cancer patients.

Involves a patient’s own mononuclear cells transformed into ‘cancer-fighting’ Dendritic cells.

Targets only the cancer cells without harming the healthy ones.
Slows the spread of cancer, prevents relapse and gives quality life to most patients.

What is Denvax Cancer Immunotherapy? ⬇️ 

- DENVAX is Personalized Treatment in Cancer 
  Involves a patients own mononuclear cells transformed into “cancer-fighting” cells 

- DENVAX is Dendritic Cell- based Cancer Immunotherapy 
  Dendritic cells are Immune cells that help in the Immune recognition process, absent in cancer patients. 

- DENVAX is Targeted Therapy 
  Targets only the cancer cells without harming the healthy ones. 

- DENVAX is Safe and Effective treatment to Prolong Life 
  Slows the spread of cancer, prevents relapse and gives quality life to most patients.
